cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and text mining, which are typically covered in the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The focus on syntactic parsing and sentence simplification further supports these sub-categories.
